Movie Management (Admin):

POST /movies: Add a new movie/showtime.
PUT /movies/:id: Update a movie/showtime.
DELETE /movies/:id: Remove a movie/showtime.
Seat Management (Admin):

POST /seats: Define seat layout and pricing.
PUT /seats/:id: Update seat layout/pricing.
Seat Availability (User):

GET /seats/:showtimeId: Get seat availability for a showtime.
POST /booking: Reserve selected seats.